    public abstract class AbstractCommandButton
extends AbstractActionComponent
implements org.richfaces.component.MetaComponentResolver, AccesskeyProps

    The <a4j:commandButton> component is similar to the JavaServer Faces (JSF) <h:commandButton> component, but additionally includes Ajax support.

      • getImage

        public abstract String getImage()
        Absolute or relative URL of the image to be displayed for this button. If specified, this "input" element will be of type "image". Otherwise, it will be of the type specified by the "type" property with a label specified by the "value" property

      • getTabindex

        public abstract String getTabindex()
        This attribute specifies the position of the current element in the tabbing order for the current document. This value must be a number between 0 and 32767. User agents should ignore leading zeros
